              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">A good study in why governance-heavy systems still fail agents when auth ceremony and runtime complexity stay too high.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/blog/twilio-api-autopsy" class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-navy/60 p-4 hover:border-slate-700 transition-colors">
