          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Inspect-only is a real trust class only while the surrounding runtime keeps identity, visible tools, and backend authority separate. These pages carry the read-only story into the remote and permissioned control plane instead of stopping at the word read-only.
          </p>
